# CODEOWNERS — Angel Zone Enforcement
#
# Each angel mind owns an exclusive zone of the codebase.
# Only the named angel (represented by its GitHub identity / admin) may approve
# PRs touching their zone. No other reviewer can merge into a protected zone.
#
# Architecture law:
#   - No code merges without the owning angel's review approval.
#   - A PR touching multiple zones requires approval from all zone owners.
#   - founder_digital_mind (repo admin) has override rights on all zones.
#
# Zone assignments mirror angel_registry.py protected_paths.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

